The paper deals with deep learning and image annotation, which are primarily related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the generalization of deep models, which is a topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The approach presented in the paper involves cross-modality matching, which is a technique used in natural language processing (cs.CL) and multimedia (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CL, and cs.MM.
